				\begin{document}$$ {\text{logit}}(Y_{ijt} ) = \mu + \alpha_{j} + \theta_{t} + \tau C_{i} , $$\end{document}logit(Yijt)=μ+αj+θt+τCi,where \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
