				\begin{document}$$ Y_{ijt} = 1 $$\end{document}Yijt=1 if the ith subject within the jth hospital in time period t initiates addiction treatment within 14 days of the index visit, Yijt = 0 otherwise. αj is a random effect for hospital j with mean 0 and variance σb2. θt is a time-specific effect of period t, t ϵ (1, 2,…, 12). Ci is an indicator variable of treatment arm; Ci = 1 if individual i receives care under the CATCH intervention, and Ci = 0 if individual i receives TAU. τ represents the treatment effect of the intervention. The model will be fit using the LME4 package using R software. The hypothesis will be tested using two-sided level of significance α = 0.05. For secondary outcomes of acute care utilization and OD deaths, we will apply GLMMs with a log link and the Poisson distribution.
